# FILE: .../studentDashboard/learningVault/myBookmarks.desc
# ROLE: The Student’s Personal Knowledge Repository
# VIBE: Organized / High-Accessibility / Minimalist Archive

## 1. THE QUICK-ACCESS HEADERS (The Filter Row)
- **TABS:** [ 📚 All ] | [ 📝 Summaries ] | [ 🧪 Exams ] | [ 🎓 Academy Courses ].
- **SEARCH BAR:** "Filter my saved resources..." (Real-time filtering of the list below).
- **SORTING:** [ 📅 Recently Saved ] | [ 🔠 Alphabetical ] | [ 📂 By Faculty ].

## 2. THE BOOKMARKED RESOURCE GRID
- **VISUAL:** A 3-column grid of "Data Cards" with 1px borders.
- **CARD COMPONENTS:**
    - **TYPE ICON:** (e.g., PDF icon for Library, Play icon for Academy).
    - **TITLE:** "Structural Analysis II - Solved 2025."
    - **METADATA:** "Faculty: Civil Engineering | Year: 3".
- **WONDER FEATURE:** **"One-Click Read"** — A button that opens the Google Drive link directly in the `documentReader.desc` without leaving the dashboard.

## 3. THE "EXAM PREP" COLLECTIONS (Folders)
- **LOGIC:** Allows the student to group bookmarks into custom "Collections."
- **EXAMPLES:** [ ✍️ Final Exams Prep ] | [ 📖 Midterm Summaries ].
- **INTERACTION:** Drag-and-drop resources into these folders for 90-degree organization.

## 4. THE PROGRESS TRACKER (Academy Sync)
- **FOR COURSES:** If a bookmarked item is from `halabAcademy`, show a small progress bar.
- **LABEL:** "Progress: 65% Completed."
- **ACTION:** [ ▶️ Resume Lesson ].

## 5. THE "CONTRIBUTION" NODE (Contributor Status)
- **LOGIC:** If the student has uploaded files that were approved by the Admin.
- **STAT:** "You have contributed **12** resources to the community."
- **XP REWARD:** "Total Contribution XP: **+600**."

## 6. THE MANAGEMENT BAR (Bottom Sticky)
- **ACTION:** [ 🗑️ Clear Selected ] | [ 📥 Download All Links (CSV) ].
- **NOTE:** "Bookmarks are synced across your devices. Challenge Every Day."